f100.description: Tangy and flavorful Punjabi Kadhi Pakora has deep fried pakoras (fritters) dunked in a tangy yogurt based curry.
f100.name: Kadhi Pakora

f101.description: Chana chaat is a tasty, tangy and easy variety of chaat snack made with white chickpeas (chana or chole), spices, herbs, onions & potato.
f101.name: Channa Chat

f102.description: Lobia Chaat is a delicious, healthy chaat made with black-eyed peas (lobia) and a lot of vegetables along with crunchy bits of tomato, cucumber and onions giving a perfect texture.
f102.name: Lobia Chaat

f103.description: Chapli Kebab or Kabab, a Pashtun-style minced kebab, usually made from ground beef, mutton or chicken with various spices in the shape of a patty.
f103.name: Chapli kabab

f104.description: Naan with kababs a traditional food containing Skinless chicken thighs, naan, yogurt, cucumber, garam masala.
f104.name: Naan Kababs

f105.description: Mutton Korma is a popular mutton curry made of mutton, onions, tomatoes, yoghurt, coriander, ginger.
f105.name: Mutton Korma

f106.description: Paye is a traditional food containing Trotters or hoof (goat or sheep), onions, tomatoes, garlic, curry powder and other spices.
f106.name: Siri Paye

f107.description: Nihari is a stew consisting of slow-cooked meat, mainly shank meat of lamb, mutton and goat meat, along with bone marrow. It is flavored with long pepper, a relative of black pepper.
f107.name: Nihari

f108.description: Aloo keema (also called keema aloo) is a traditional Pakistani dish made using ground Minced beef and potatoes.
f108.name: Aloo Qeema

f109.description: Aloo gosht is a meat curry consisting of potatoes cooked with meat, usually beef, in a stew-like shorba gravy.
f109.name: Aloo Gosht

f11.description: A delicious bread sandwich containing marinated chicken pieces fried with sauces and spices.
f11.name: Chicken Sandwich

f110.description: Deep-fried, crispy fish fingers in which strips of fish are coated in a batter made of gram flour and some spices and then deep-fried in hot oil till crunchy.

f111.description: Tangy fish in a spicy, thick and delicious masala that adds a kick to your seafood cravings. Made from fresh ingredients, Fish Masala is must.

f112.description: Tandoori fish in which whole fish is marinated in yogurt and in spice lemon marinate which is then grilled to smoky and charred. The charred texture add so much flavour into the fish. Simple marination like chilli powder, cumin, turmeric, chaat masala, tandoori masala, lemon and yogurt make it super delicious.
f112.name: Tandoori Fish

f113.description: Spicy Steamed Fish mainly contains White fish fillets, fish sauce, spicy lime, fish stock and lime juice.
f113.name: Spicy Steamed Fish

f114.description: Grilled fish steak in which fish fillets are grilled after marinating it with herbs, lemon juice, and aromatic spices.
f114.name: Grilled Fish Steaks

f115.description: Mustard Roasted Fish made of Red snapper, dijon mustard, whole grain mustard, capers & black pepper.
f115.name: Mustard Roasted Fish

f116.description: Masala Fish Curry made of Fish, Coconut milk, tamarind, tomato, corn powder & curry leaves.
f116.name: Masala Fish Curry

f117.description: Fish Cutlets a great snack that tastes too good. Goes well with tartar sauce. Fish Cutlet has a slightly different taste from the usual cutlets. They are made with the combination of tuna fish, fresh herbs , spices and bread crumb coating.

f118.description: A snack made of a pastry dough which is quite similar to the african meat pie and the Chicken Pie Pastry and wrapped in a spicy Fish filling.
f118.name: Fish Roll

f119.description: Fish Kebab made of Potatoes, bread crumbs, pangasius, green chilies, lemon (a healthy food).
f119.name: Fish Kabab

f12.description: An egg fried bread sandwich with onion omelete, perfect for a healthy breakfast.
f12.name: Egg Sandwich

f120.description: Chicken soup is a soup made from chicken, simmered in water, usually with various other ingredients. This classic chicken soup consists of a clear chicken broth with pieces of chicken or vegetables, common additions are pasta, noodles, dumplings, or grains such as rice and barley.
f120.name: Chicken Soup

f121.description: Lentil soup is a soup based on lentils, it include vegetarian or meat, and consists of brown, red, yellow, green or black lentils, with or without the husk. Dehulled yellow and red lentils disintegrate in cooking, making a thick soup.
f121.name: Lentil Soup

f122.description: Tomato soup, a soup with tomatoes as the primary ingredient. It is served hot or cold. It is smooth in texture, and includes chunks of tomato, cream, chicken or vegetable stock, vermicelli, chunks of other vegetables and meatballs.
f122.name: Tomato Soup

f123.description: Beef barley soup taste's deeply beefy, and loaded with chunks of tender, flavorful meat, plump grains of barley, and aromatic vegetables.
f123.name: Beef Barley Soup

f124.description: Chicken Rice Soup contains Skinless chicken thighs, ribs, grain white rice, chicken broth and carrots.
f124.name: Chicken Rice Soup

f125.description: Mushroom soup is a simple type of soup where a basic roux is thinned with cream or milk and then mushrooms and/or mushroom broth are added.
f125.name: Mushroom Soup

f126.description: A healthy version of Chicken Corn soup with desi chicken contains Creamed corn, soy sauce, boiled eggs, fish crackers & chili paste.
f126.name: Chicken Corn Soup

f127.description: Corn Vegetable Soup mainly contains some mixed vegetables, Sweet corn, beans, spring onion, corn flour & ginger.
f127.name: Corn Vegetable Soup

f128.description: A delicious cheesey potato soup made from Potatoes, cheddar cheese, milk, chicken bouillon & celery.
f128.name: Potato Cheese Soup

f129.description: Pumpkin Soup is made of Squash, pumpkin seeds, double cream, olive oil & chicken stock.
f129.name: Pumpkin Soup

f13.description: A fried sandwich containg deep fried fish with lemon, sauces and spices.
f13.name: Fish Sandwich

f130.description: Vegetable Soup contains Mixed vegetables, Apple cider vinegar, potato, tomato paste, red pepper flakes & carrots.
f130.name: Vegetable Soup

f132.description: Lassi is a regional name for buttermilk, a traditional dahi-based drink. Lassi is a blend of yogurt, water, spices and fruit. Namkeen lassi is similar to doogh, while sweet and mango lassis are like milkshakes. Lassi is infused with cannabis in the form of bhang.
f132.name: Lassi

f133.description: Most of us like sipping on doodh-wali-chai because of the flavour or just out of habit. Adding milk in tea looks like a perfect option.
f133.name: Tea with Milk

f134.description: Rooh Afza called as refresher of the soul. It contains Rooh afza syrup, sabja seeds, sugar & ice cubes.
f134.name: Rooh Afza

f135.description: Rabri Doodh contains Condensed milk, milk powder, cream, almonds, Pistachio, jaggery & sugar.
f135.name: Rabri Doodh

f136.description: A falooda is a cold dessert made with noodles. Traditionally it is made by mixing rose syrup, vermicelli, and sweet basil seeds with milk, often served with ice cream.
f136.name: Falooda

f137.description: Lemon soda is a blend of lemon juice with icecubes, salt, sugar and chilled soda. It is a carbonated soft drink made with lemon juice.
f137.name: Lemon Soda

f138.description: Lemon Tea is a refreshing tea where lemon juice is added in black or green tea. It soothes the throat, prevents cough and congestion, and helps in weight loss.
f138.name: Tea With Lemon

f139.description: Grape juice is obtained from crushing and blending grapes into a liquid. The sugars in grape juice allow it to be used as a sweetener or vinegar.
f139.name: Grape Juice

f14.description: A sandwich containing slighty fried vegetables like capsicums, carrots, potatoes and cucumber with spices and sauces.
f14.name: Vegetable Sandwich

f140.description: Lemon water is the juice of the lemon fruit combined with water and drunk hot or cold, with additions such as lemon zest, honey, mint or spices like turmeric or cayenne pepper.
f140.name: Lemon Water

f141.description: Mineral water helps keep your heart healthy and working properly. It's a clear, fresh water.
f141.name: Mineral Water

f142.description: A sweet, carbonated cola with little mouthfeel or aftertaste. Coca Cola is less harsh than Pepsi, and has a vanilla taste which is not found in Pepsi. There are also lesser tastes of cinnamon and nutmeg.
f142.name: Coca Cola

f143.description: Fanta is a brand of fruit-flavored carbonated soft drinks.
f143.name: Fanta

f144.description: Sprite is a colorless, lemon and lime-flavored soft drink.
f144.name: Sprite

f145.description: Apple juice is a fruit juice made by the maceration and pressing of an apple. Apple juice mainly contains Apples, cinnamon & sugar.
f145.name: Apple Juice

f146.description: Sooji or semolina halwa is roasted in clarified butter or ghee and is cooked with water and ghee. Sometimes adding milk instead of water make it rich & sometimes it contains a mixture of water and milk.
f146.name: Halwa

f147.description: Barfi or burfi is a basic fudge made from full fat milk, sugar and ghee. A thick consistency of barfi was pressed down in a tray, garnished with nuts and cut to squares and rectangles called barfi.
f147.name: Barfi

f148.description: Gulab jamun is a milk-solid-based sweet, a type of mithai popular as national dessert of Pakistan.
f148.name: Gulab Jamun

f149.description: Ras Malai an amazing sweet dish, which is super-soft and is enjoyed with saffron milk. Ras malai consists of flattened balls of chhena soaked in malai (clotted cream) flavoured with cardamom. Milk is boiled and a bit of vinegar or lime juice is added to split it.
f149.name: Ras Malai

f15.description: A Grilled Sandwich containing Boneless chicken breast, Red bell pepper, white bread, butter, lettuce and green pepper.

f150.description: Simply delicious, comforting, creamy & rich, kheer is a perfect dessert anytime you crave for something sweet. Kheer contains Basmati rice, saffron, golden raisins, sugar, cashews, rose water, sweet, nuts & blanched almonds.

f151.description: Halwa Puri is one unique comfort food containing Puri, halwa, chapati flour, mixed nuts, coarse semolina.
f151.name: HalwaPuri

f152.description: Jalebi a popular sweet snack. Jalebi is a spiral shaped crisp & juicy sweet made with all-purpose flour, gram flour and sugar syrup.
f152.name: Jalebi

f153.description: Tutti frutti is a colorful confectionery containing various chopped and usually candied fruits, or an artificial or natural flavouring simulating the combined flavour of many different fruits.

f154.description: Doodh Dulari is one of popular Pakistani Food. It is combination of thick milk, colored vermicelli & cham cham.

f155.name: Chocolate Browine

f156.description: Fruit trifle is usually made up of various layers, normally there is a cake which lines the bottom of the bowl, followed by fruit, jelly, custard, or pudding mixture, jelly, more fruit, and topped off with a generous layer of freshly whipped cream.
f156.name: Fruit Trifle

f157.description: Shahi Tukra (with Condensed Milk), a popular hyderabadi special sweet is a royal treat to taste buds at anytime. Shahi tukda a dessert made with ghee fried bread, thickened sweetened milk, saffron and nuts.

f158.description: Ice-cream flavoured with the King of Fruits! Mangoes impart a luscious creamy texture and rich flavour to this delicious frozen dessert. Mango Ice Cream contains Whipping cream, Sweetened condensed milk, canned mango pulp & mango.

f159.description: Vanilla is frequently used to flavor ice cream. Vanilla ice cream, like other flavors of ice cream, is Smade by cooling a mixture made of cream, sugar, and vanilla above a container of ice and salt.

f16.description: A Sandwich of bread (traditionally toasted), sliced cooked poultry, ham or fried bacon, lettuce, tomato, chicken and mayonnaise.

f165.description: Strawberry Ice Cream contains strawberries (fresh), milk, heavy cream, sugar & vanilla extract.

f166.description: Espresso coffee can be made with a wide variety of coffee beans and roast degrees.
f166.name: Espresso

f167.description: A cappuccino is an espresso-based coffee drink and is prepared with steamed milk foam. Variations of the drink involve the use of cream instead of milk, using non-dairy milk substitutes and flavoring with cinnamon or chocolate powder.
f167.name: Cappuccino

f168.description: A latte macchiato is milk marked with an espresso. latte macchiato is served in a tall glass and has distinctive layers between the foam, espresso and milk with the foam on top, espresso below the foam and milk at the bottom.
f168.name: Latte Macchiato

f169.description: Black coffee is a beverage made from roasted coffee beans. It Contains creamer, milk, sugar, or sweetener in coffee for making it creamy, which reduces the bitter flavor. Black coffee is also used as the base of many drinks, including cappuccinos, lattes, and macchiatos.
f169.name: Black Coffee

f17.description: A Cheese sandwich that has been cooked on the grill long enough for the cheese to melt a little and the bread to get brown and a little crispy and healthy.

f170.description: Hot chocolate, also known as hot cocoa or drinking chocolate, is a heated drink consisting of shaved chocolate, melted chocolate or cocoa powder, heated milk or water, and usually a sweetener like whipped cream or marshmallows.
f170.name: Hot Chocolate

f171.description: Iced coffee is a coffee beverage served cold. It is prepared by brewing coffee normally and then serving it over ice or in cold milk, or by brewing the coffee cold. In hot brewing, sweeteners and flavoring may be added before cooling, as they dissolve faster.
f171.name: Iced Coffee

f172.description: Chicken Wings contains Butter, flour, chicken wingettes, garlic powder & black pepper.

f173.description: A very popular fast food restaurant item. A chicken nugget consists of a small piece of deboned chicken meat that is breaded or battered, then deep-fried or baked.

f174.description: French fries, chips, finger chips, French-fried potatoes, or simply fries, are batonnet or allumette-cut deep-fried potatoes. They are prepared by cutting the potato into even strips, then drying and frying it, usually in a deep fryer.

f175.description: Hot shot are chicken pieces marinated with spicy ingredients, battered and then finally fried. It tastes good with Chili sauce, chili garlic sauce & tomato sauce.

f180.name: Raita

f181.description: A salad is a dish consisting of mixed, mostly natural ingredients with at least one raw ingredient.

f182.description: Ketchup or catsup is a type of table condiment with a sweet and tangy flavor typically refers to tomato ketchup. Original ketchup used egg whites, mushrooms, oysters, grapes, mussels, or walnuts, among other ingredients.

f183.description: Naan is a leavened, oven-baked or tawa-fried flatbread.

A bottom layer, most often consists of a crust or base made from crushed cookies, graham crackers, pastry, or sometimes sponge cake.
